frontmatter.title: OpenShift Commons Gathering London
frontmatter.lead_text: This OpenShift Commons Gathering will be held on July 6th live in London, England
frontmatter.info_text: This OpenShift Commons Gathering will be held in-person and all talks will be delivered live! As always, our focus is on creating a welcoming and inclusive space for peer-to-peer interactions online. This Gathering will focus on talks from and by Cloud Native practitioners with production deployments sharing their use cases, insights into their workloads and lessons learned along the way.
frontmatter.event_footer_text: This Gathering will be held on British Summer Time (BST)

schedule.session_name: Welcome to the Commons: Unlock the Potential of Collaboration
What’s Next for Cloud Natives Living on the Edge
AMA Session: Live Q/A with Guest Speakers, Red Hat Engineers & Project Leads
